          | Noteshare is a platform for creating and sharing documents on the web
          | – course materials and lecture notes, handbooks, film festival catalogues,
          | the next great novel, you name it!
          | <br>
          | <br>
          | <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/vschool%2Fnoteshare_images/rockband.jpg" alt="rockband" width="200">
          | <br>
          | <br>
        p.compact.message == link_to 'More about Noteshare', '/about'

        span style='color:#F5574F;position:absolute; bottom:1em;left:2.5em;' ❤
        i style='color:#F5574F;position:absolute; bottom:1em; left:4.0em;' Share the knowledge!

